OL,3,CFinancial pressures for NHS Dumfries
OL,4,Cand Galloway as cost savings required
OL,6,FDumfries and Galloway NHS has
OL,7,Fexplained their "very stark financial
OL,8,Fsituation" as a deficit could rise to
OL,9,Fup to #54million by March 2025.
OL,11,FThe health board say, while other
OL,12,Fboards in the country are facing a
OL,13,Fsimilar position, they wanted to
OL,14,Fexplain to the public about the "scale
OL,15,Fof the challenge."
OL,17,FThe financial position in April 2024
OL,18,Fis expected to be at a deficit of
OL,19,F#35million.
