OL,3,CFinancial pressures for NHS Dumfries
OL,4,Cand Galloway as cost savings required
OL,6,FThe increased figure of #54million is
OL,7,Fdue to inflation, growing patient need
OL,8,Fand increasing costs involved in
OL,9,Fproviding treatment and care.
OL,11,FIn a statement said: "NHS Dumfries and
OL,12,FGalloway have agreed with Scottish
OL,13,FGovernment that we are required to
OL,14,Freduce the deficit to #25 million by
OL,15,Fthe end of March 2025 which equates to
OL,16,Fachieving savings of #29 million
OL,17,Fwithin the coming financial year.
OL,19,F"This will be a very difficult target
OL,20,Fto meet, representing about 8% per
OL,21,Fcent of NHS baseline budget.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
