OL,3,CFinancial pressures for NHS Dumfries
OL,4,Cand Galloway as cost savings required
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, we have no option but
OL,7,Fto progress towards the achievement of
OL,8,Fthese necessary savings, and it is
OL,9,Fimportant that we are open and honest
OL,10,Fwith our population and our staff, and
OL,11,Fthat they understand the scale of this
OL,12,Fchallenge.
OL,14,F"While we will do everything we can to
OL,15,Fmitigate the impact, we recognise that
OL,16,Four services will feel different for
OL,17,Four staff, patients and communities.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
