OL,3,CFinancial pressures for NHS Dumfries
OL,4,Cand Galloway as cost savings required
OL,6,F"It is still too early to be able to
OL,7,Fdescribe the detail of how these
OL,8,Fsavings will be achieved. The scale of
OL,9,Fthe savings means that a very large
OL,10,Famount of work is required to deliver
OL,11,Fthe agreed target. These savings are
OL,12,Flikely to impact on our workforce, our
OL,13,Finfrastructure and our ways of
OL,14,Fdelivering services.
OL,16,F"However, the Board has committed to
OL,17,Fkeep staff, public and partner
OL,18,Fagencies up to date with the progress
OL,19,Ftowards this savings target, and there
OL,20,Fwill be regular updates to Board
OL,21,Fthroughout the year.
