OL,3,CFinancial pressures for NHS Dumfries
OL,4,Cand Galloway as cost savings required
OL,6,F"Organisationally, we will seek to
OL,7,Fcontinue our engagement with staff and
OL,8,Fcommunities about how we can best
OL,9,Fdeliver services in the face of this
OL,10,Funprecedented challenge."
OL,12,FDr Iain Kennedy, chair of BMA
OL,13,FScotland, said: "This sadly does not
OL,14,Fcome as a huge surprise and follows
OL,15,Fconsistent warnings from Audit
OL,16,FScotland about the financial
OL,17,Fsustainability of the NHS.
