OL,3,CFinancial pressures for NHS Dumfries
OL,4,Cand Galloway as cost savings required
OL,6,F"These funding cuts will be a massive
OL,7,Fconcern for patients and staff in
OL,8,FDumfries & Galloway which like the
OL,9,Frest of Scotland is facing into
OL,10,Fsoaring consultant vacancies,
OL,11,Fincreased waiting times with the
OL,12,Ffuture for primary care remaining
OL,13,Funclear.
OL,15,F"Today's news confirms fears that the
OL,16,F#550m increase specifically for NHS
OL,17,Fboards outlined in December's Scottish
OL,18,FGovernment budget would not be
OL,19,Fsufficient.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
