OL,3,CFinancial pressures for NHS Dumfries
OL,4,Cand Galloway as cost savings required
OL,6,F"We were aware at the time that the
OL,7,FScottish Government had suggested the
OL,8,Fconsolidated position for all NHS
OL,9,FBoards at month six of 2023-24 was a
OL,10,Fforecast deficit of #395 million.
OL,12,F"It is another reminder why the
OL,13,FScottish Government must urgently
OL,14,Fprogress its commitment to hold a
OL,15,FNational Conversation to help shape
OL,16,Fthe future of Scotland's NHS.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
