OL,3,CFinancial pressures for NHS Dumfries
OL,4,Cand Galloway as cost savings required
OL,6,F"Ministers must ensure it is an open,
OL,7,Fhonest and transparent conversation
OL,8,Fthat includes cross party and public
OL,9,Finput, as well as the views of the NHS
OL,10,Fworkforce. By doing so ` we can
OL,11,Ffinally start establishing what
OL,12,Fultimately we are asking of our NHS
OL,13,Fand whether funding is indeed
OL,14,Fsufficient."
OL,16,FScottish Health Secretary Neil Gray
OL,17,Fsaid: "We are providing over #14.2
OL,18,Fbillion for NHS Boards in 2024-25 to
OL,19,Fsupport services, a real terms
OL,20,Fincrease of almost 3%.
