OL,6,F"This comes against the backdrop of
OL,7,Fthe UK government's autumn statement
OL,8,Fwhich set out a real terms cut for NHS
OL,9,FEngland for 2024-25, with only #10.8
OL,10,Fmillion of additional consequentials
OL,11,Fderived from health spending `
OL,12,Fequivalent to 0.06% of Scotland's
OL,13,Fhealth budget.
