OL,4,Cand Galloway as cost savings required
OL,6,F"Despite our significant investment,
OL,7,FNHS Boards, like other public
OL,8,Fservices, are under unprecedented
OL,9,Fpressure as a result of UK Government
OL,10,Fausterity, inflation, Brexit and Covid
OL,11,Fand we are continuing to work with
OL,12,Feach Board to recover and reform
OL,13,Fservices and address the financial
OL,14,Fchallenge this year and beyond."
